                            <comment id="14468378" author="roshandawrani" created="Sun, 29 Nov 2009 00:42:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think it is a bug - when the final variable is static, it should be allowed to be set in static constructor - same as instance level final variables are allowed to be set in non-static constructors.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14468242" author="blackdrag" created="Sun, 29 Nov 2009 04:32:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;arg, no, that was not intended... the exclusion filter is not handling static consructors it seems.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14468379" author="roshandawrani" created="Sun, 29 Nov 2009 10:52:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
